Babil iyo Baabuloon [2] [3] [4] (Arabic: محافظة بابل Muḥāfaẓa Bābil) waa guddoomiye ku yaal bartamaha Ciraaq. Waxay leedahay meel 5,119 kilomitir oo isku wareeg ah (1,976 sq m), iyada oo lagu qiyaasey dad lagu qiyaasey 1,651,565 qof 2002-dii. [5] Caasimadda gobolka waa magaalada Hillah, oo ka soo hor jeedda magaaladii hore ee Baabil (BAL), oo ku taal Webiga Euphrates.
